The paper proposes a new machine learning algorithm for pattern classification, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm is applied to image classification datasets, which also falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of k-nearest neighbor rule, which is a common technique in neural networks and computational intelligence (cs.NE) and statistical learning (cs.SI).
